{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "马如龙醉酒后向大婉求婚，大婉以自嘲回应。马如龙醒来后发现自己在苏小婉的住处，小婉是邱凤城深爱的女子，原为怡芳院妓女，被邱凤城脱籍后独居于此。小婉告知邱凤城逾期未归，她已抱定殉情之念。马如龙深受感动，承诺三日内找到邱凤城的下落。离开后，马如龙察觉小婉房中花瓶与丫鬟的矛盾线索，怀疑事有蹊跷。返回时竟听到房中有男人笑声，翻墙而入发现一名穿考究靴子的玄衣男子与小婉对峙，小婉以死相胁，真相扑朔迷离。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你嫁给我好不好？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么要我嫁给你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "因为我知道你对我很好，因为别人都怀疑我，把我当作杀人的凶手，都想杀了我，只有你信任我，只有你，肯帮我的忙。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你要我嫁给你，只不过因为你喝醉了，等你清醒的时候，就会后悔的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "等你看见比我好看的女人，你更会后悔得要命。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我又丑又怪又凶，比我好看的女人也不知道有多少。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你就是马公子？‘白马公子’马如龙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "前几天你是不是也在寒梅谷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你见到了邱凤城？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "你也认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我姓苏，叫小婉，我就是你要找的人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "这里是什么地方？我怎么会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "是一位俞五爷送你来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "俞五爷说你不但是凤城的朋友，而且只有你知道他的行踪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "这里是你的家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我没有家，这地方不能算一个家。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我本来只不过是城里怡芳院的一个……一个妓女，从小没爹没娘，凤城为我脱了籍，替我买了这栋房子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是，他若不在这里，这里又怎么能算一个家？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "想不到他真的是个这么多情的人！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他的脾气虽然刚强，却是个心地善良的人，从来不肯做一点对不起别人的事。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他对我更好，处处都为我着想，从来都没有看轻过我，一个像我这样的女人，能够遇到他这样的男人，我……我死也瞑目了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "你们还年轻，怎么会死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是你若来迟一步，现在就已看不到我。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他临走时就已跟我约好，至迟昨晚上一定会回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "如果他没有回来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那就表示他已经离开了人世，我当然也要陪他一起去。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "幸好他还没有死。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那么现在他的人在哪里？为什么还不回来？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道他如果没有死就一定会回来，你又何必骗我？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "其实你用不着骗我的，我只要知道，他也跟我一样痴，我就已心满意足了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在天已快黑了，孤男寡女，瓜田李下，我也不敢再留马公子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "我知道你的决心，我并不想勉强你，但是我希望你能等三天，三天之内，我一定有邱凤城的消息告诉你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "好，我再等三天。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ya_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小丫头",
      "listener": "char_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "大奶奶，咱们也买两盆梅花回去好不好？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ya_tou",
      "text": "不好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ya_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小丫头",
      "listener": "char_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "这些花又不贵，买点回去看看有什么不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ya_tou",
      "text": "因为我没有这种心情。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ya_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小丫头",
      "listener": "char_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "大奶奶也真是的，大爷也只不过两三天没回来，大奶奶就连看花的心情都没有了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的要我死？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yi_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衣男子",
      "listener": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "text": "你以为我不敢？你以为我怕你？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "苏小婉",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yi_nan_zi",
      "text": "好，你要我死，我就死给你看。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    }
  ],
